# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# UBUNTU SERVER (192.168.160.118) — fully automatic, no SSH needed
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Ollama and Charlie RAG are both systemd services — they start
# automatically on boot. No manual intervention required.
#
# If you ever need to check them manually via SSH:
# Check RAG health:         curl http://192.168.160.118:8001/health
# Check RAG stats:          curl http://192.168.160.118:8001/stats
# RAG service status:       sudo systemctl status charlie-rag
# Restart RAG service:      sudo systemctl restart charlie-rag
# Ollama service status:    sudo systemctl status ollama
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# LAPTOP (Django) — the only command you need to run
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Development (you only):   uvicorn config.asgi:application --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --reload
# Production (team access): uvicorn config.asgi:application --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
#
# Utility commands:
# Skip startup (migrations): DJANGO_SKIP_READY=1 python manage.py migrate
# Collect static files:      python manage.py collectstatic